<figureCitation id="13242A30D70C835AFB1FFDE6FB554017" box="[1156,1234,590,616]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[136,229,2028,2050]" captionTargetBox="[273,1314,197,1991]" captionTargetId="figure-18@2.[261,1327,187,2001]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Astragalus vogelii subsp. fatimensis Maire:A, A twig with flowers; B, A. twig with pods." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5540493" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5540493/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="213">Figs. 1</figureCitation>
&amp; 
